contentrichtext.text: '''M90''' or '''M-90''' may refer to: * [[M90 (camouflage)]], a camouflage pattern used by the Swedish armed forces * [[M-90 (Michigan highway)]], a state highway in Michigan * [[M90 motorway]], a motorway in Scotland * [[Barrett M90]], a bullpup sniper rifle * [[Lotus M90]], a concept car * [[Volvo M90 transmission]], a gearbox for the Volvo 940 models * [[Zastava M90]], a Yugoslav modern assault rifle ; shortening or designation for : * [[McDonnell Douglas MD-90]] * [[Messier 90]] (M90), a spiral galaxy in the Virgo cluster * [[Mendota Airport]] (FAA location identifier: M90), an airport in Mendota, California {{Letter-NumberCombDisambig}}
